  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promotion of BAT and BEP to Reduce uPOPs Releases from Waste Open Burning in the Participating African Countries of COMESA-SADC Subregions</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.  uPOPs baseline information on open burning practices and inventory of major  dumpsites/landfills in participating countries   ,2.  Regulatory / Legal framework review, policy development and institutional strengthening ,3. Pilot demonstration  of BAT/BEP in selected priority sites,4.  Information dissemination and awareness raising ,5.  Monitoring and  evaluation of results,Project Management Cost</narrative>
